author: Patrick Cc:
description:
Labubu dolls look like harmless toys, but their rise has exposed something much darker about consumer culture. Fueled by celebrity endorsements, artificial scarcity, and obsessive fandom, these creepy little figurines have turned into overpriced status symbols that people are literally committing crimes to get them..
